title: Chapter 1285 - Save Me, Ancestor!
volume_title: His Sword Takes Aim A The Three Thousand Worlds Of The Stars, Suppressing Foes Both Past And Present
body:
Chapter 1285 - Save Me, Ancestor!

All of these Cosmic Enlightenment Realm World Kings hailed from peak factions, and each controlled a star realm’s supreme Celestial Law. Their foundations were firm, their treasures shocking. All of them were far beyond ordinary cultivators of the same realm.

But Su Yi broke through nineteen Cosmic Enlightenment World Kings’ joint attack in a single slash!

Wei Shan watched from within the immortal palace. Even he, who was more familiar with the Temple Master than just about anyone, was unwittingly stunned.

He’s just a reincarnation, and he barely has Heavenly Longevity Realm cultivation, so how is he this strong?

The word ‘fierce’ is insufficient to describe him!

But Su Yi found it a bit of a pity.

He’d poured all of his strongest methods into that slash, holding nothing back.

But in the end, he had only managed to break their joint attack, that’s all. And here he’d thought he’d determine victory and defeat in a single slash.

“Everyone, I warned you a long time ago that he’s most likely an old schemer hiding his cultivation base. He’s trying to make us complacent, disguising himself as a pig so he can eat a tiger!” Feng Yunlie said icily. “I’m sure you can see it now too. If we don’t use everything we’ve been...
